name: Master Archery Birds: Sky Hunt
description:
Master Archery Birds: Sky Hunting is a simple amazing and interesting archery shooting game using bow and arrow. Your goal is to shoot birds. So, let’s play this archery wild hunting and kill the flying birds.
Feature :
- Realistic sound effects
- Cutting Edge Graphics
- Excellent animation.
- Accurate physics effects
- Challenging objectives to achieve
- Beautiful themes
- Easy to play, hard to master game
- Smooth Bird animations.
